  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 425\u00b0F (218\u00b0C).",
    "Combine butter, icing sugar, and flour in a mixing bowl. Mix until a dough forms.",
    "Sprinkle the dry ingredients over the butter mixture and mix again until combined thoroughly.",
    "Transfer the mixture to an ungreased baking dish, pressing it down evenly to form a crust.",
    "Bake for 12-15 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Let cool completely before slicing."
